      "content": "The main draw is that the neural-symbolic approach is way more efficient with compute and much more reliable for logic-heavy technical docs. It basically eliminates the \"hallucination\" issues we sometimes see with LLMs because it follows strict symbolic rules. The board thinks it's a much safer and more streamlined way to handle global comms.",
